function newEnhancedScene(){ensureSceneCommandCenterV102();const p=currentProject(),e=currentEpisode();if(!p)return toast('先に作品を選択してください');if(!e)return toast('先に話数を選択してください');const s=normalizeCommonItem({id:uid('scene'),projectId:p.id,episodeId:e.id,title:'',sceneTitle:'',sceneOverview:'',summary:'',scenePurpose:'',sortOrder:Math.max(0,...(state.scenes||[]).filter(x=>x.episodeId===e.id).map(x=>+x.sortOrder||0))+1,production:{status:'未着手',priority:'中',assignee:'',checklist:{}},productionStage:'未着手',storyArchiveCardIds:[],relatedCharacters:[],usedImageIds:[],imageSetIds:[],usedVideoIds:[],audio:{bgm:'',se:'',voice:''},vidu:{japanesePrompt:'',englishPrompt:''},productionLink:{dashboardId:'',externalId:'',syncStatus:'local-only',schema:'scene-production-v1'}},'scene');state.scenes.push(s);saveState(true);editSceneCommand(s.id)}
